1 A BILL FOR AN ACT relating to the Military Code; to amend section 55-117,
2 Reissue Revised Statutes of Nebraska; to change provisions relating
3 to the ordering of the Nebraska National Guard into active combat;
4 to provide a duty; to require a report; to define a term; to
5 harmonize provisions; and to repeal the original section.
6 Be it enacted by the people of the State of Nebraska,
